# Project Structure Guide

This is a Kubernetes operator project for multicluster role assignment management built with operator-sdk.

## Key Directories:

- [cmd/main.go](mdc:cmd/main.go) - Main entry point for the operator
- [api/v1alpha1/](mdc:api/v1alpha1/) - API types and CRD definitions
- [internal/controller/](mdc:internal/controller/) - Controller logic
- [config/](mdc:config/) - Kubernetes manifests and Kustomize configurations
- [test/](mdc:test/) - Test files and test utilities

## Important Files:

- [go.mod](mdc:go.mod) - Go module dependencies
- [Makefile](mdc:Makefile) - Build and deployment commands
- [PROJECT](mdc:PROJECT) - Operator SDK project configuration
- [Dockerfile](mdc:Dockerfile) - Container image definition
- [Dockerfile.rhtap](mdc:Dockerfile.rhtap) - Enhanced RHTAP/Konflux container image with FIPS compliance

## Configuration:

- CRD definitions in [config/crd/bases/](mdc:config/crd/bases/)
- RBAC in [config/rbac/](mdc:config/rbac/)
- Sample resources in [config/samples/](mdc:config/samples/)

## Konflux Integration:

- Pipeline definitions in [.tekton/](mdc:.tekton/)
- ReleasePlanAdmission in [multicluster-role-assignment-rpa.yaml](mdc:multicluster-role-assignment-rpa.yaml)
